text: @amazon Logistics confirmed for me tonight by phone and email that it is perfectly acceptable for a delivery driver to mark a package delivered and NOT deliver it - and I am just supposed to wait for it. @USPS @UPS @FedEx what are your policies on falsified deliveries?

@UPS @UPSHelp My package was supposed to be delivered between 10-2. Then it changed to 3. Now it changed to “End-Of-Day”. Why even tell me an estimated delivery time when you can’t honor it? This is a business package that I will now no longer receive during business hours.

@howlingthunder I'm sorry for the confusion. Is this going to a business or residential location? Please DM the tracking number, your phone number and confirmation of the delivery address to my team so, we can assist you. ^RN https://t.co/wKJHDXWGRQ
